org.apache.poi.poifs.filesystem

Enum FileMagic

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<FileMagic>
      • org.apache.poi.poifs.filesystem.FileMagic
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<FileMagic> 

    public enum FileMagic
extends java.lang.Enum<FileMagic>
    The file magic number, i.e. the file identification based on the first bytes of the file(文件幻数，即基于文件第一个字节的文件标识)

      • valueOf

        public static FileMagic valueOf(java.io.File inp)
                         throws java.io.IOException
        Get the file magic of the supplied File

        Even if this method returns UNKNOWN it could potentially mean, that the ZIP stream has leading junk bytes

        (获取提供的文件的文件魔法即使此方法返回UNKNOWN，也可能意味着ZIP流具有前导垃圾字节)
        Parameters:
        inp - a file to be identified(inp -待识别的文件)
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException(java.io.IOException)

      • valueOf

        public static FileMagic valueOf(java.io.InputStream inp)
                         throws java.io.IOException
        Get the file magic of the supplied InputStream (which MUST support mark and reset).

        If unsure if your InputStream does support mark / reset, use prepareToCheckMagic(InputStream) to wrap it and make sure to always use that, and not the original!

        Even if this method returns UNKNOWN it could potentially mean, that the ZIP stream has leading junk bytes

        (获得所提供的InputStream的文件魔力（必须支持标记和重置）。如果不确定您的InputStream是否支持标记/重置，请使用DeliverToCheckMagic（InputStream）将其包装起来，并确保始终使用它，而不是原始的！即使此方法返回UNKNOWN，也可能意味着Zip流具有领先的垃圾字节)
        Parameters:
        inp - An InputStream which supports either mark/reset(inp -支持标记/重置的InputStream)
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException(java.io.IOException)

      • prepareToCheckMagic

        public static java.io.InputStream prepareToCheckMagic(java.io.InputStream stream)
        Checks if an InputStream can be reset (i.e. used for checking the header magic) and wraps it if not(检查InputStream是否可以重置（即用于检查标题魔法），如果不能，则将其包装)
        Parameters:
        stream - stream to be checked for wrapping(stream -要检查包裹的流)
        Returns:
        a mark enabled stream(启用标记的流)
